Good Day Lady that answer phone at Yummy Tacos, You need to be aware , courtesy goes a long way. To continue a flourishing , positive and  lucrative business sometimes you need to give.  TO keep customers happy and wanting to come back more for your good food , you also have to give good service.  Extra  salad dressing (Ranch) without charging is not impossible , and rather professional and smart. Since the salad is big and delicious a nice size portion for the dressing is adequate.  The first time I ordered the Tostada Salad with grilled chicken and ranch dressing , I did receive the same size as the other 2 French dressings size. Then the next time I received a smaller container . Quite disappointed but enjoyed the salad.  Due to the lack of your customer service ,  busy fussing over we don’t sell it like that and I have to charge extra…blah blah blah  .I am looking into finding another business that sells food as Yummy Tacos. Good Customer Service goes a long way… Suggestion replace the phone lady with a pleasant and business minded person, you would have recieved 5 stars .
